channel.title: [PI] jar'ing my client to make webclient
channel.description:
Im trying to make a webclient and my client.jar wont load it says this -
"Sorry, an error has occurred whilst loading cursedpkz. To fix this try the following(in order) 1.Close all browser windows and reloading 2.Try clearing cache 3.Try using different game world 4.Try rebooting your computer 5.Try selecting a different version of Java from the play game menu"
use this url to see what i mean - http://cursedpkz.webs.com/webclient.htm thats the same client.jar file just uploaded to webclient umm i have no idea how to fix this can some please help me !!!!!!!!! i will pay some1 if they can give me a working solution for this error or who can fix it for me with teamviewer THIS IS THE TUT I FOLOWED - http://www.google.org/runescape-development/rs2-client/tutorials/253018-how-make-your-project-insanity-client-webclient.html this is my client! http://www.mediafire.com/?gx8gh9do3v8t7qv if any1 could try make a webclient out of my client and get it working i will happly pay them for the fix, working webclient or jar'ed version of my client that works from what i can afford this client download is the version before i changed file's to auto download my cache from this url - http://www.mediafire.com/?kyntorl51w05f6k client dl http://www.mediafire.com/?gx8gh9do3v8t7qv ALSO I JUST TESTED SOMETHING - I FOUND OUT THAT IF I PUT THE CLIENT.JAR WITH CACHE AND RAW FOLDER I WORKS PERFECT AS SOON AS I SPLIT THEM UP THEY STOP this is the folder it has my client.jar and raw files 608kb http://www.mediafire.com/?r4ahwoo1cr63oaa
